            <html:p>
  A distributive lattice is <html:em>Noetherian</html:em> if it satisfies the equivalent conditions in <fr:link href="/idem-comm-G598/" title="Equivalent Noetherian condition" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-G598/" display-uri="idem-comm-G598" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-G598/" display-uri="idem-comm-G598" /></fr:link>.
</html:p>
